programme.desc: Bob Ross helps a timid little stream find its way to a delightful waterfall, while gazing upon a forest of elegant trees.

programme.title: Barn at Sunset
programme.desc: Bob Ross paints an expansive barn appearing half-covered in a snowy setting of frost bitten foliage and sun-kissed sky.

programme.title: By the Sea
programme.desc: Come visit the coast with Bob Ross and paint a glorious ocean-scape; enjoy the solitude and gentle rhythm of the waves caressing the shoreline.

programme.title: Indian Summer
programme.desc: Paint along with Bob Ross and discover what autumn beauty unfolds as those exotic orange and gold colors appear on canvas.

programme.title: Blue Winter
programme.desc: Travel with Bob Ross to the middle of winter, where shades of indigo create the stark reality of the season. You’d better bundle up for this one!

programme.title: Desert Glow
programme.desc: Follow along with Bob Ross as he takes you into the incredible beauty of the dry lands.

programme.title: Lone Mountain
programme.desc: Travel with Bob Ross and enjoy a spectacular view -- this painting presents a fabulous lesson in creating rugged and rocky natural surfaces.

programme.title: Florida’s Glory
programme.desc: Bob Ross presents an intriguing painting with an outline of the ‘sunshine state’, and then creates a lovely beach setting within the borders.

programme.title: Autumn Images
programme.desc: Feel the soft coolness of late summer air and drink in the beauty of changing colors with Bob Ross as he creates this refreshing masterpiece.

programme.title: Hint of Springtime
programme.desc: Melting snow from the mountains creates a rushing flow of water into a valley just awakening for spring. Feel the crisp new season with Bob Ross.

programme.title: Around the Bend
programme.desc: Join Bob Ross on a painting excursion along this beautiful scenic river – who knows what abundance of nature’s wealth lies beyond!

programme.title: Countryside Oval
programme.desc: Travel with Bob Ross to a picturesque spot in the meadow and delight in the discovery of not one, but two serene fishing holes.

programme.title: Winding Stream
programme.desc: Join Bob Ross for a stroll down yonder by the river, relax in the serenity of an expansive yet quiet sky with proud evergreens looking on.

programme.title: Tranquility Cove
programme.desc: As the foliage reaches its peak of autumn beauty, experience the tranquility of nice meadow, pond and happy birch tree. All painted the Bob Ross way!

programme.title: Cabin in the Hollow
programme.desc: Soft misty background, sweet snow-kissed cabin and rich trees and bushes – all nestled down inside a winter oval painting by Bob Ross.

programme.title: View from Clear Creek
programme.desc: Gently rolling mountains make an amazing backdrop for this Bob Ross masterpiece; a winding stream and textured ground vegetation provide the rest.

programme.title: Bridge to Autumn
programme.desc: Take a drive into the country with Bob Ross and pass through an old covered bridge into a landscape bursting with soft fall foliage.

programme.title: Trail’s End
programme.desc: In this oval painting, Bob Ross creates a wonderful scene where an old fence follows a trail to the edge of the woods.

programme.title: Evergreen Valley
programme.desc: Drive through mountain country with Bob Ross and happen upon a ridge of thick, rich evergreens gracing the hollow below.

programme.title: Balmy Beach
programme.desc: Bob Ross invites you for a walk on the shore; soothing waves rolling in from the sea to the plam trees – all in a delightful seashell shape on canvas.

programme.title: Lake at the Ridge
programme.desc: Guest artist Steve Ross extends an invitation to join him on the banks of a crystal loch for a view of majestic mountain peaks.

programme.title: In the Midst of Winter
programme.desc: It’s a cold, cold winter day but Bob Ross offers a warm and roomy barn as refuge from the snowy blanket covering the farm.

programme.title: Anatomy of a Wave
programme.desc: Guest Artist Joyce Ortner captures the true beauty of the ocean waves, blue and enchanting in this breathtaking seascape masterpiece.

programme.title: The Windmill
programme.desc: Bob Ross creates a proud strong windmill, standing in watch beside old farm buildings where happy little animals lay still in the night.

programme.title: Autumn Glory
programme.desc: In this landscape Bob Ross paints a far away mountain snuggled in with bright green trees and bushes mirrored in glistening waters.

programme.title: Indian Girl
programme.desc: Guest artist Ferne Sirois shares her own American Indian heritage in this adorable portrait of a playful, smiling little child.

programme.title: Meadow Stream
programme.desc: Bob Ross paints a beautiful summer scene today – rushing little riverlet flowing through the luscious greenery of a cabin landscape.

programme.title: Meadow Lake
programme.desc: Glide into this scenic world of green trees and bushes reflecting into calm waters. Bob Ross paints both gentle beauty and almighty power.

programme.title: Winter Sun
programme.desc: Find the glistening sun peeking through the trees in this wintery scene; Bob Ross creates a cold day warmed by daystar radiance.

programme.title: Mountain Splendor
programme.desc: It’s almost fall, and Bob Ross captures the undaunted power and charm of a mighty brown mountain surveying its rustic surroundings.

programme.title: Lake by the Mountain
programme.desc: Talented guest painter Steve Ross shows you how to create a mirror-like lake spanning the width of snowy peaks and foothills.

programme.title: Mountain Glory
programme.desc: Layers and layers of mountains, as far as the eye can see -- Bob Ross shows us the secret to creating a larger-than-life landscape.

programme.title: Grey Winter
programme.desc: Bob Ross uses monochromatic tones to convey the icy coldness of a silvery lake surrounded by lacy trees and bushes – brr!

programme.title: Dock Scene
programme.desc: An abandoned shipping boat hugs a pier in a water scene that Bob Ross completes with some charming old dockside storage sheds.

programme.title: Dark Waterfall
programme.desc: Watch Bob Ross create a sweet little waterfall in the middle of a protective forest of glorious early autumn foliage.

programme.title: Misty Rolling Hills
programme.desc: Bob Ross creates soft purple sky and tall trees that almost seem to float in the hazy foothills of a distant, blue-grey mountain.

programme.title: Lakeside Cabin
programme.desc: A cabin has found a peaceful resting place amongst a warm setting of lush, lakeside greenery in this wonderful oval creation by Bob Ross.

programme.title: Warm Winter Day
programme.desc: The field of snow and the little cabin yield to the bright, orange sun -- Bob Ross conveys harmony in this cold, but cozy scene.

programme.title: Waterside Way
programme.desc: A wilderness path leads you to the side of a still lake in a setting that Bob Ross accents with an abundance of trees.

programme.title: Hunter’s Haven
programme.desc: Bob Ross’ exciting use of blue, yellow and orange hues brings vibrancy to this wood side setting and dream cabin beside a clear blue lake.

programme.title: Bubbling Mountain Brook
programme.desc: A playful brook appears the perfect complement to a range of rugged mountains in this Bob Ross setting on canvas.

programme.title: Winter Hideaway
programme.desc: Bob Ross puts a lonesome cabin in the middle of a snowy setting as an unexpected place of respite for the weary traveler.

programme.title: Winter Hideaway
programme.desc: Bob Ross puts a lonesome cabin in the middle of a snowy setting as an unexpected place of respite for the weary traveler.

programme.title: Foot of the Mountain
programme.desc: A lake and some tall trees pay homage to a commanding mountain in the background, as a cabin stands nearby -- a classic Bob Ross creation.

programme.title: Russet Winter
programme.desc: The first snowfall just beyond autumn signals the true beginning of winter -- join Bob Ross as he discovers just such a glorious moment.

programme.title: Purple Haze
programme.desc: Catch a glimpse of the sun trying to break through shades of soft crimson, shining its golden touch upon the land.

programme.title: Double Take
programme.desc: Bob Ross presents a really unique idea using black gesso -- two lovely paintings in one -- summer and winter scenes overlapping on the same canvas!

programme.title: Deep Wilderness Home
programme.desc: Bob Ross takes you far into the untouched forest to discover an old country home on a cliff, completely hidden by surrounding foliage.

programme.title: Tranquil Dawn
programme.desc: Join Bob Ross on a warm winter morning, the surroundings still undisturbed by Nature’s little creatures.

programme.title: Wintertime Blues
programme.desc: Bundle up with artist Bob Ross and peer into the north country in the midst of winter; experience a vision in the coldest of azure tones.

programme.title: Serenity
programme.desc: Breaking the silence of a misty morning is a rippling brook through the forest. Join Bob Ross as he takes you to this favorite escape.

programme.title: Country Creek
programme.desc: Team up with Bob Ross and travel back to the days of swimming in that lovely secluded river bend; bring back memories of a forgotten time.

programme.title: Mountain Rhapsody
programme.desc: Experience the blissful pleasure of the coldest season under a splendid pastel sky with Bob Ross; enjoy this fabulous mountain masterpiece.

programme.title: Wilderness Cabin
programme.desc: Paint along with Bob Ross and discover the beauty of a secluded log home with only quiet pond and rustic trees for companionship.

programme.title: Wilderness Day
programme.desc: Step into the natural beauty of an overgrown colorful mead and enjoy the peace and soft tranquility you get from Bob Ross’ painting technique.

programme.title: Through the Window
programme.desc: A cleverly constructed shape on canvas! Peek through the panes with artist Bob Ross and share a beautiful snowy day outside.

programme.title: Delightful Meadow Home
programme.desc: Hike into the expanse of wilderness with Bob Ross and happen upon a quaint little home sitting among softly blowing meadow grasses.

programme.title: Mountains of Grace
programme.desc: Join guest artist Steve Ross today -- experience the magnificence of splendid mountains and glassy lake embraced by leafy trees and bushes.

programme.title: Lake in the Valley
programme.desc: Discover a beautiful quiet lake hidden deep in the wilderness - and just beyond a glorious snow-covered mountain.

programme.title: A Cold Spring Day
programme.desc: Painter Bob Ross invites you to enjoy the last of winter’s snowy touch on canvas, as mountains and valleys begin to emerge from their slumber.

programme.title: Evening’s Glow
programme.desc: Enjoy the golden radiance of a setting sun with Bob Ross as night hastens over a softly blended knoll – you’ll be home at last, just down trail’s end.

programme.title: Snow Birch
programme.desc: An incredibly unique Bob Ross painting -- delight in the effects of white and black gesso, discover a birch tree forest.

programme.title: Reflections of Calm
programme.desc: Bob Ross takes you to a beautiful lake in high country -- catch a glimpse of magnificent mountains, images echoed in the crystal clear water below.

programme.title: Tranquil Wooded Stream
programme.desc: Bob Ross takes you to a lovely spot deep in the woods where the seclusion, silence and beauty offer serenity to the soul.

programme.title: Ebony Sea
programme.desc: As the night settles over a rocky coast, Bob Ross gives you a warm glow still in the sky – a painting achieved on black canvas.

programme.title: Shades of Grey
programme.desc: Bundle up and endure the cold weater in this snow filled adventure; Bob Ross paints a wintry mountain scene using only Grey and White tones.

programme.title: Autumn Splendor
programme.desc: The fall breeze rustles in the trees as you rest your feet in crisp still waters. Discover the joys of nature in this Bob Ross painting.

programme.title: Black River
programme.desc: In this painting Bob Ross emphasizes a slow river winding around colorful foliage, with the final embers of sunlight ahead.

programme.title: Brown Mountain
programme.desc: Swim in the warm water, nap in the luxurious green grass – today Bob Ross creates a wonderful summer mountain scene.

programme.title: Reflections
programme.desc: Truly picture perfect. A bright day and still water combine to make amazing mirrored images throughout this Bob Ross mountain masterpiece.

programme.title: Black & White Seascape
programme.desc: An approaching storm and dramatic sky set the mood for this unique seascape. Bob Ross uses a canvas painted half black and half white.

programme.title: Majestic Pine
programme.desc: Bob Ross paints a golden field of sparse pines and other greenery inside the unique shape of a tapered rectangle with cut-in corners.

programme.title: Cactus at Sunset
programme.desc: A path of cacti and rocks lead right up to a bold sun setting in a dramatic red sky, all from the delicate motions of Bob Ross’ paint brush.

programme.title: Mountain Range
programme.desc: Guest painter Steve Ross uses lots of color in this stirring depiction of giant peaks behind foothills opening onto a smooth lake.

programme.title: Lonely Retreat
programme.desc: A real Bob Ross favorite – he uses blue and red highlights to accentuate the drama and beauty of a snow-bound cabin at sunset.

programme.title: Northern Lights
programme.desc: Bob Ross begins with a black canvas to create this startling rendition of a snowy landscape with the notorious lights of the northern sky.

programme.title: Winter Evergreens
programme.desc: Join Bob Ross as he creates a beautiful snowy landscape with stately evergreens, warmed by winter sun hanging low over distant mountains.

programme.title: Surf’s Up
programme.desc: Feel the salt spray as Bob Ross paints ocean waves under abundant clouds, rolling in to spend their energy against sand and rock.

programme.title: Red Sunset
programme.desc: Warm light in sky and clouds makes this a glowing, fiery landscape -- Bob Ross teaches the use of his technique on black canvas.

programme.title: Meadow Road
programme.desc: Majestic snow-covered peaks and evergreens loom over lush green grasslands as Bob Ross takes you into his world of natural beauty.

programme.title: Winter Oval
programme.desc: A beautiful mountain painting in an oval – with a surprising twist! – as Bob Ross creates a lonely cabin embraced by lovely lacy bushes.

programme.title: Secluded Beach
programme.desc: Bob Ross teaches us the secret of his wet-on-wet technique while creating a restless ocean crashing against a rugged rocky coastline.

programme.title: Forest Hills
programme.desc: Strong mountains, proud evergreens and luxurious trees and bushes hug the velvety smooth foothills in today’s Bob Ross masterpiece.

programme.title: Little House by the Road
programme.desc: A weathered fence guards a rustic country home shadowed by tall trees as Bob Ross creates another masterpiece in his unique style.

programme.title: Retrato de Sally
programme.desc: El artista visitante, Ben Stahl, utiliza un método de pintura más tradicional para resaltar el tímido encanto de una niña.

programme.title: Cascada con niebla
programme.desc: Bob Ross ayuda a un tímido arroyo a encontrar su camino hacia una encantadora cascada, mientras contempla un bosque de elegantes árboles.

programme.title: Granero al atardecer
programme.desc: Bob Ross pinta un extenso granero que aparece semicubierto en un entorno nevado de follaje mordido por la escarcha y un cielo bañado por el sol.

programme.title: Junto al mar
programme.desc: Ven a visitar la costa con Bob Ross y pinta un glorioso paisaje oceánico; disfruta de la soledad y del suave ritmo de las olas acariciando la costa.

programme.title: Verano indio
programme.desc: Pinta junto a Bob Ross y descubre la belleza otoñal que se despliega cuando esos exóticos colores naranja y dorado aparecen en el lienzo.

programme.title: Invierno azul
programme.desc: Viaja con Bob Ross a la mitad del invierno, donde los tonos añiles crean la cruda realidad de la estación. Será mejor que se abrigue para esta ocasión

programme.title: Resplandor del desierto
programme.desc: Sigue a Bob Ross mientras te lleva a la increíble belleza de las tierras áridas.

programme.title: Montaña solitaria
programme.desc: Viaja con Bob y disfruta de una vista espectacular -- esta pintura presenta una lección en la creación de superficies naturales escarpadas y rocosas.

programme.title: La gloria de Florida
programme.desc: Bob Ross presenta una intrigante pintura con un contorno del estado del sol, y luego crea un encantador escenario de playa dentro de los límites.

programme.title: Imágenes de otoño
programme.desc: Siente el frescor del aire de finales de verano y disfruta de los colores cambiantes con Bob Ross mientras crea esta refrescante obra maestra.

programme.title: Un toque de primavera
programme.desc: La nieve que se derrite en las montañas crea una corriente de agua en un valle que acaba de despertar la primavera. Sienta la nueva estación con Bob

programme.title: Alrededor de la curva
programme.desc: Acompaña a Bob para pintar a lo largo de este hermoso y pintoresco río - ¡quién sabe qué abundancia de riqueza de la naturaleza se encuentra más allá!

programme.title: Óvalo de campo
programme.desc: Viaje con Bob Ross a un pintoresco lugar de la pradera y deléitese con el descubrimiento no de uno, sino de dos serenos pozos de pesca.

programme.title: Arroyo sinuoso
programme.desc: Acompaña a Bob en un paseo por el río, relájate en la serenidad de un cielo amplio pero tranquilo con los orgullosos árboles de hoja perenne mirando.

programme.title: Cala de la tranquilidad
programme.desc: A medida que el follaje alcanza su belleza otoñal, experimenta la tranquilidad de un prado, un estanque y abedules, todo pintado a la manera de Bob

programme.title: Cabaña en la hondonada
programme.desc: Suave fondo de niebla, dulce cabaña besada por la nieve y ricos árboles y arbustos - todo anidado dentro de una pintura ovalada de invierno de Bob

programme.title: Vista desde Clear Creek
programme.desc: Unas montañas onduladas son el increíble telón de fondo de esta obra de Bob; un arroyo sinuoso y la vegetación del suelo con textura aportan el resto

programme.title: Puente hacia el otoño
programme.desc: Adéntrate en el campo con Bob Ross y pasa por un viejo puente cubierto a un paisaje repleto de suave follaje otoñal.

programme.title: Fin del sendero
programme.desc: En este cuadro ovalado, Bob Ross crea una maravillosa escena en la que una vieja valla sigue un sendero hasta el límite del bosque.

programme.title: Valle de Evergreen
programme.desc: Conduce a través de las montañas con Bob Ross y encuentra una cresta de espesos y ricos árboles de hoja perenne que adornan la hondonada de abajo.

programme.title: Playa Balmy
programme.desc: Bob te invita a pasear por la orilla; las olas llegan desde el mar hasta los árboles de plama, todo ello en una forma de concha marina sobre lienzo

programme.title: Lago en la cresta
programme.desc: El artista invitado Steve Ross le invita a unirse a él en las orillas de un lago cristalino para contemplar los majestuosos picos de las montañas.

programme.title: En pleno invierno
programme.desc: Es un día de invierno muy frío, pero Bob Ross ofrece un granero cálido y espacioso como refugio del manto de nieve que cubre la granja.

programme.title: Anatomía de una ola
programme.desc: La artista invitada Joyce Ortner captura la belleza de las olas del océano, azules y encantadoras en esta obra maestra de paisaje marino.

programme.title: El molino de viento
programme.desc: Bob crea un fuerte y orgulloso molino de viento, que vigila junto a los edificios de la granja donde los animalitos se quedan quietos en la noche.

programme.title: Gloria otoñal
programme.desc: En este paisaje, Bob Ross pinta una montaña lejana acurrucada con árboles y arbustos de un verde brillante que se reflejan en aguas resplandecientes.

programme.title: Chica india
programme.desc: La artista invitada Ferne Sirois comparte su propia herencia india americana en este adorable retrato de un niño juguetón y sonriente.

programme.title: Arroyo de la pradera
programme.desc: Bob Ross pinta hoy una hermosa escena veraniega: un riachuelo que fluye a través de la exuberante vegetación de un paisaje de cabañas.

programme.title: Lago en la Pradera
programme.desc: Planea sobre este mundo escénico de árboles y arbustos verdes que se reflejan sobre las tranquilas aguas. Bob Ross pinta una gentil belleza y una impactante fuerza.

programme.title: Sol Invernal
programme.desc: Encuentra el sol brillante deslumbrando a través de los árboles en este escenario invernal; Bob Ross crea un día frío entibiado por esta radiante estrella.

programme.title: Esplendor de la montaña
programme.desc: Es casi otoño, y Bob Ross capta el poder y el encanto impertérritos de una poderosa montaña marrón que vigila su rústico entorno.

programme.title: Lago junto a la montaña

programme.desc: Low turkey numbers and a few trespassers made this season tougher than normal. John hits a couple states in pursuit of a few gobblers, but ends up not punching his last tag for a reason that is not to common and often not discussed in conservation circles.

programme.title: RMEF - "Better Than We Found It"
programme.desc: “Part of our responsibility as citizens in this country is to make sure we not only take care of these resources but we hand it off to the next generation in better condition that we found it.” -Bob Ziehmer, Senior Director of Conservation for Bass Pro Shops & Cabela's Join Bob in New Mexico as he talks about taking care of our natural resources for future generations. Special thanks to Express UU Bar Ranch

programme.title: "North America Deer Slam- Texas Gulf Coast Whitetail"
programme.desc: Mark Peterson continues his quest for the North American Deer Slam, with his next destination being Texas. This time, he sets his sights on the Gulf Coast Whitetail. In March of 2023, Mark was in Texas pursuing Nilgai with the same outfitter. Witnessing the abundance of deer in the area, he was determined to return and cross the Gulf Coast Whitetail off his list. Bagging this buck will mark the achievement of 11 out of the 31 species on his list.

programme.title: "North America Deer Slam- Montana Whitetail"
programme.desc: Mark Peterson persists in his pursuit of the North American Deer Slam, joined by his close friend and WTA client, Kevin Burmeister. Their focus is now set on pursuing a Northwestern Whitetail in the picturesque landscapes of Montana. This is Mark’s second attempt at this particular subspecies, with his initial endeavor taking place in Saskatchewan – a contrast in hunting styles. In Saskatchewan, they utilized ground blinds, while in Montana, the strategy is centered around the art of spot and stalk. One of the aspects that Mark finds particularly captivating about the Deer Slam is the diverse hunting styles each state employs, adding a unique dimension to his hunting experiences.

programme.title: "Inspiration and Motivation with Coach HP"
programme.desc: Join me for an exclusive interview with Coach HP as we embark on an incredible journey with a true sports aficionado. Born in Cuba and driven by an unwavering passion for baseball, Coach HP's life story is a remarkable odyssey from Miami to Los Angeles and beyond. - Growing up under the guidance of a strict yet devoted father, he imbibed the value of hard work, a cornerstone of his extraordinary success today. After his baseball days in high school and college, Coach HP headed to the West Coast, where he explored a world beyond the diamond. - His path is marked by intriguing twists, including influential roles in entertainment and nightlife, as well as becoming a sought-after national speaker. Yet, at the core of it all, baseball has been his heart's true calling. In 2016, Coach HP returned to Miami with a fresh training approach that's revolutionizing the game. Join us for this enlightening conversation where we not only uncover the lessons learned in baseball but also gain insights into life's profound journey. It's a story of passion, hard work, and the relentless pursuit of excellence that you won't want to miss - Prepare to be inspired, entertained, and motivated. programme.title: Stoked on Fishing - An Unforgettable Trip, South Lake, Part Two
programme.desc: This show was filmed in late October of 2019. Four months prior, in June of 2019, Tim Carnahan was diagnosed with Glioblastoma, Brain Cancer. According to Tim's medical team, his life expectancy could be between three months and 18 months. Fast forward to now, 2020; today's update is one we hoped would never come. With a heavy heart and tear-filled eyes, we share with you that Tim Carnahan has passed away after battling for close to 12 months. It only fits that the last words to pass his lips were I love you, Lory, and keep fishing. While his time on earth was cut short, the amount of joy he experienced and shared with others was genuinely tremendous and will never be forgotten. If you would like to help out in any way, lory and friends have put together a Go Fund Me page to ease the financial burden of medical bills and afford lory some time to greave and transition into life without Tim. We love you, Tim. Rest in peace, buddy.

When the girl's parents are brutally murdered, a kung fu master known as the Silver Fox takes the girl under his wing and teaches her some choice killing techniques. Soon, the girl learns that the prince is being threatened by the same marauders who killed her parents. Now, it's time for revenge!

Battling it out to the death are two teams of rival combatants: Plato, a crazed Asian killer and his henchman Steve; and Mickey, the washed-up ex-champion and his loyal friend Jim, a fierce fighter from Sydney. Who will emerge victorious?
